title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Is That A Missile?
description: A reality show caught a missile launch on camera… and thought that it was coming for them. And Demi Lovato is opening up about that song “29” that everyone thinks is about dating Wilmer Valderrama when he was 29 and she was 17.
